text: Hrux phwk cea khid wa phwk cea ca thuk plxy wi doy thi xallxhˌ yang midi thrng ru brrda phu thi txsu nı hmu phwk cea læa midi yudthux pheuxn snith xun ca kxallxhˌ læa rx sul khxng phraxngkh læa xun cak phu sraththa thanghlay læa xallxhˌ nan thrng rxbru xyang laxeiyd nı sing thi phwk cea kratha
